    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf33\" data-dest-detail=\"[51,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,233.967,null]\">Question #23</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf33\" data-dest-detail=\"[51,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,205.467,null]\">You have a Microsoft\n                        365 tenant that uses Microsoft Exchange Online and Microsoft Defender for Office 365.What\n                        should you use to identify whether zero-hour auto purge (ZAP) moved an email message from\n                        the mailbox of a user?</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf34\" data-dest-detail=\"[52,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,752.64,null]\">Explanation</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf34\" data-dest-detail=\"[52,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,550.14,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
