    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfce\" data-dest-detail=\"[206,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,771.467,null]\">Question #101</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfce\" data-dest-detail=\"[206,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,742.967,null]\">You have a Microsoft\n                        365 E5 subscription that uses Microsoft Defender for Endpoint.You need to identify any\n                        devices that triggered a malware alert and collect evidence related to the alert. The\n                        solution must ensure that you can use the results to initiate device isolation for the\n                        affected devices.What should you use in the Microsoft 365 Defender portal?</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfce\" data-dest-detail=\"[206,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,487.967,null]\">Explanation</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfce\" data-dest-detail=\"[206,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,367.967,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd0\" data-dest-detail=\"[208,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,771.467,null]\">Question #102</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd0\" data-dest-detail=\"[208,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,742.967,null]\">HOTSPOT -You have a\n                        Microsoft 365 E5 subscription that uses Microsoft Purview and contains a user named\n                        User1.User1 shares a Microsoft Power BI report file from the Microsoft OneDrive folder of\n                        your company to an external user by using Microsoft Teams.You need to identify which Power\n                        BI report file was shared.How should you configure the search? To answer, select the\n                        appropriate options in the answer area.NOTE: Each correct selection is worth one point.</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd1\" data-dest-detail=\"[209,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,785.64,null]\">Explanation</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd1\" data-dest-detail=\"[209,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,347.575,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd2\" data-dest-detail=\"[210,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,491.293,null]\">Question #103</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd2\" data-dest-detail=\"[210,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,462.793,null]\">You have the\n                        resources shown in the following table.You have an Azure subscription that uses Microsoft\n                        Defender for Cloud.You need to enable Microsoft Defender for Servers on each resource.Which\n                        resources will require the installation of the Azure Arc agent?</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd3\" data-dest-detail=\"[211,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,719.64,null]\">Explanation</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd3\" data-dest-detail=\"[211,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,599.64,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd3\" data-dest-detail=\"[211,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,340.684,null]\">Question #104</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd3\" data-dest-detail=\"[211,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,312.184,null]\">You have an Azure\n                        subscription that uses Microsoft Defender for Cloud.You have a GitHub account named Account1\n                        that contains 10 repositories.You need to ensure that Defender for Cloud can access the\n                        repositories in Account1.What should you do first in the Microsoft Defender for Cloud\n                        portal?</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd4\" data-dest-detail=\"[212,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,785.64,null]\">Explanation</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfd4\" data-dest-detail=\"[212,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,665.64,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
