    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfed\" data-dest-detail=\"[237,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,603.184,null]\">Question #116</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfed\" data-dest-detail=\"[237,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,574.684,null]\">You have an Azure\n                        subscription that uses Microsoft Defender for Cloud.You have an Amazon Web Services (AWS)\n                        subscription. The subscription contains multiple virtual machines that run Windows\n                        Server.You need to enable Microsoft Defender for Servers on the virtual machines.Which two\n                        actions should you perform? Each correct answer presents part of the solution.NOTE: Each\n                        correct answer is worth one point.</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfed\" data-dest-detail=\"[237,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,244.684,null]\">Explanation</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pfed\" data-dest-detail=\"[237,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,124.684,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
