    "<a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf10c\" data-dest-detail=\"[268,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,472.684,null]\">Question #130</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf10c\" data-dest-detail=\"[268,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,444.184,null]\">You have a custom\n                        analytics rule to detect threats in Azure Sentinel.You discover that the analytics rule\n                        stopped running. The rule was disabled, and the rule name has a prefix of AUTO DISABLED.What\n                        is a possible cause of the issue?</a> <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf10c\" data-dest-detail=\"[268,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,267.184,null]\">Explanation</a>\n         <a class=\"l\" href=\"#pf10c\" data-dest-detail=\"[268,&quot;XYZ&quot;,62.25,114.184,null]\">Community\n                        Discussion</a>",
